{"id": "1369157501706043413", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "Dear Keepers,\n\nThe global version of Morimens is approaching its 1.5-Year Anniversary! The B.I.A.V Team could not have made it this far without your great support. We are excited to introduce a series of optimizations in the upcoming 1.5 Anniversary Version Update. The preview will be divided into three parts: Combat Optimizations, System Optimizations, and Events & Rewards, with details coming in later announcements.\n\nPlease note: The following battle adjustments are still in the Final Beta phase. Further changes may be made based on feedback and testing. Final content will be confirmed in the official release.\n\n[Awakener Soulforge Aptitude Enhancements]\nRamona, Lotan, Ogier, Doll, Aigis, and Erica will receive their own unique Soulforge Aptitude Enhancements, helping them play a stronger role in Astral Reign challenges.\n\n[All Realms Posse Enhancement]\nThe Keyflare limit for all Realms will be increased to match Pure Chaos, allowing a second use of Special Posse each turn for more flexible planning. Pure Chaos' unique trait will be adjusted to: \"The second use of Special Posse can be triggered twice,\" making Keyflare management even more crucial in this Realm.\n\n[Aequor Realm Tentacle Enhancement]\nA new effect is being added to Surging Tides Stance: If active at the end of a turn, a Tentacle will spawn at the start of the next turn. Additionally, once the Tentacle Limit is reached, further Tentacle generation will increase the limit, though the required number of generations will gradually rise. This change strengthens Tentacle-focused teams and further differentiates the three Aequor stances.", "timestamp": "2025-05-06T03:43:06.123000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": true, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1369157515270422599", "channel_id": "1368890341490556948", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "[Faded Legacy Difficulty Lowered]\nThe difficulty of Chapter 8 and the Final Chapter (Normal Mode) will be reduced, allowing players to clear them without relying heavily on meta teams. In the future, the most challenging combat content will be reserved for Hard Mode and the D-Effect Zone.\n\n[Astral Reign Difficulty Lowered]\nThe 15-turn limit in Astral Reign's main story stages will be removed, enabling clears with Emergency Gnosis. Additionally, Counter and Poison damage will now scale with the number of Roused units in the team (up to 200%), improving their performance even without investing in enhancement items or effects.\n\n[D-Effect Zone Bonus Points]\nAn extra team challenge opportunity per wave will be added, granting up to 5 additional points (max 25 points). This change offers more high-score potential without altering difficulty or rewards. Note: This change is being disclosed in advance. It will arrive in Version 2.3, not the 1.5 Anniversary update.", "timestamp": "2025-05-06T03:43:09.357000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": true, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "rich2", "emoji_id": "1357181559945564170", "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368890341490556948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～战斗增强篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
